keyFacts: A subpoena was issued on September 30, 2021, for records related to aircraft with tail numbers N750A or N722JE from January 1, 2008, onward.
The subpoena is part of the criminal case United States v. Ghislaine Maxwell (20 Cr. 330 (AJN)).
The subpoena was issued by U.S. Attorney Audrey Strauss of the Southern District of New York.
The recipient of the subpoena is AK Title Service, Inc., commanded to appear at 40 Foley Square, Courtroom 906.
Failure to comply with the subpoena constitutes contempt of court and subjects the recipient to civil sanctions and criminal penalties.
